<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
       "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
<title>JustHost Simple Control Panel - <%= controller.action_name %></title>
<style type="text/css">
*{ margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, "宋体"; font-size: 0.85em; color: #333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;}
a { text-decoration: none; color: #E58C43; }
a:hover { background-color: #CEE7F5; text-decoration: underline; color: #549DC7; }
.clear { clear: both; }
#page { width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; }
#header { margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; height: 50px; color: #fff; line-height: 180%; text-align: left; background-color: #3399cc; padding: 10px;}
#left { float: left; width: 20%; padding-top: 10px;}
#left ul { margin: 0; padding: 0; list-style: none; border-right: 1px solid #999; border-bottom: 1px solid #999;}
#left li { padding: 5px 0px 5px 10px; width: 100%; background-color: ghost;}
#right { float: left; width: 75%; margin-left: 20px; padding: 10px; }
#frm { width: 98%; height: 50px; border: 1px dashed #999; padding: 8px 0px 8px 10px; }
#msg { font-size: 10px; color: #999; padding: 2px; }
#result { width: 98%; padding: 5px 0px 5px 12px; background-color: #0b0f22; color: #61ce3c; }
input.enter { height: 25px; width: 400px; color: blue; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="page">
	<div id="header"><h1>JustHost Ruby On Rails Simple Control Panel For No SSH Support.</h1><h3>by Elvuel</h3></div>
	<div id="left">
		<ul>
<%
	with_options :controller => controller.controller_name do
		controller.public_methods(false).sort.each do |link|
-%>
			<li><%= link_to link, :action => link %><li>
<%
		end
	end
-%>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div id="right">
		<% unless @form.to_s.empty? -%>
		<div id='frm'><%= @form -%></div>
		<% end %>
		<div id='result'><%= @result -%></div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>